mstSubtitle.serif: Mission accomplished. Here, take this. Don't waste it.
A new request has come in. There's too much going on in this apartment!

Ding dong. A notice for all you curious people. 
The next floor is open, so Master, please feel free to challenge the new missions.

Ding dong. A notice for all you curious people. 
A new location is open, so Master, please feel free to challenge the new missions.
Hmph!
There.
Haaah!
Your time in this world is over. See you in hell.

[id 602300_0_B050]Death Perception...
[id 602300_0_B051]Death is not going to get in my way!
What a bother...
Okay, you want me to do this?
Tch, you're all the same...
My turn? You really work people hard.
Finished? I'll leave the clean up to you, then.
Well, it's good to have someone worth fighting.
Ugh!
This is bad!
Look what you got me into...
I guess this is karma...
What.
That thing?
Oh brother...
Oh, I feel sick.
It's the end of the dream.

[id 602300_0_G010]So this is what you call the fruit of your labor, huh?
[id 602300_0_G011]...Not a bad feeling.
[id 602300_0_G020]One grade up... [id 602300_0_G021]There's still a long way to go, Master.
[id 602300_0_G030]Huh? Won't I get changed? [id 602300_0_G031]Everyone else wears different clothes? [id 602300_0_G032]...Heroic Spirits are quite fashionable, aren't they...

[id 602300_0_G040]Shut up. I like these clothes, I'm not changing. 
[id 602300_0_G041]I might change the kimono to a different one, [id 602300_0_G042]but I'm not changing my jacket.

[id 602300_0_G050]...What? Even I take a break sometimes. [id 602300_0_G051]Actually, this is usually how I am when I am not needed. 
[id 602300_0_G052]If it's you...then, [id 602300_0_G053]I guess it's okay to let you in my room. [id 602300_0_G054]There's more ice cream in the fridge, help yourself.

Whose birthday? Yours? I see.
...I wonder if there are any good restaurants around here... I should have checked...

It's noisy... Another strange festival, I suppose. 
Go if you want. I'll join you if I feel like it.

I'm bored. Is this Touko's office or something?
If you're feeling restless let's go out, come on.
What, a Servant? That's what I am right now. That's all right. It's easy. I'll follow your plan.
Master Servant relationship, hmm... our relationship will be good as long as you give decent instructions, won't it? I'm happy as long as you give me prey.
What do I like... Hmph, I don't know. You ask some amazing things.
What do I hate? Ah, that's clear to me. People who know their true nature, yet still lie to themselves.

A Holy Grail that grants wishes? What? That sounds so fake. 
Sales people aren't welcome at this house.

Why a kimono and leather jacket? ...Why does it matter? It's just what I feel like wearing. 
What? Not why but how I wear it? Well, there's a trick to tie the obi and with the hem...

Servant and Master, huh... I feel like there's been something like this before, but that may have been a dream. 
Here is a lot more comfortable than that time.

You're more understanding than I expected. You're an airhead, pure hearted, you speak openly, and yet your heart is strong... huh? 
...Oh, you're the same as him. It's no wonder I can't think badly of you.

...I'm stuck. I want to get back to where I was as soon as possible, but my life here isn't all bad. 
And... I can't leave you alone. I think I might have to see this through to the end...

All right, I have made up my mind!
It's all too suspicious, all this talk about Chaldea and Masters. What kind of mess has Touko gotten us into, but as they say, even a chance acquaintance is decreed by destiny. 
Please continue to take care of me, Master. I will accompany you as a guard until the day you return to your old life.

Was that me just now?
...Maybe I've been working too hard since I got here... How pathetic of me to be seeing ghosts...

You sure are an interesting fellow...
What's with that sack? You can pull food out as much as you want? No matter how exotic the food may be?
...Interesting, show us what you can do then.

So Asagami's here now, too. Huh. That's good to know.
She might seem like a dangerous woman, but she's pretty reliable.
She's a bit of a loose canon, though. So be careful.
She's incredibly opinionated, and it really doesn't take much to set her off since she's pretty lacking in empathy.
One wrong step, and things'll go sideways pretty quick.

Welcome.
Ugh, what a drag.
I'm not going to explain what's for exchange here.
Just hang around as long as you like.

Exchanging items... Are we in the stone age or something?
No, never mind.
Primitive isn't so bad...yeah...

You want that one?
I don't need to wrap it up for you, right?
Obviously we do not accept returns. Make sure you use everything, okay?

This shop sure carries a bunch of weird stuff...
Even Touko's office didn't have this much crap...

The street vendor is closing up soon.
It's just about time, but if you have anything left to exchange yet, I'll take it.

To be honest, this was my first try at a part-time job.
And I have to say, it was easy.
But Mikiya always told me to just not work as a convenience store clerk.

Yes, yes, good job. 
Are you working hard at exterminating zombies?

Welcome to the Garan no Dou♪
...Oh, you don't get it? You don't, do you? 
What am I doing...

Nights in the city are long, but there's a limit to that too. 
You can't just take your time in doing everything.

You could just keep mowing down those zombies, but read the information sometimes. 
It's an apartment, so at least look at the community boards.

Assassin-class Servant. Name's Ryougi Shiki.
...Does this work as a greeting? I guess it is a weird one huh...
I am a bit different, but I will beat the crap out of our enemies.
